  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I wish this moment could be forever.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yuto Habu, the hero with nothing to show for it, met the camera-toting heroine</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >He meets the heroine, Nazuna Fukamachi, who has a camera, on a bridge with a beautiful view by chance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cinematic novel game that is not a movie, but it is a new kind of cinematic novel game in which time flows like a movie.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is a novel game with no particular options, but we hope you will enjoy the music, illustrations, and story.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I wish this moment could be forever.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yuto Habu, the hero with nothing to show for it, met the camera-toting heroine</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >He meets the heroine, Nazuna Fukamachi, who has a camera, on a bridge with a beautiful view by chance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cinematic novel game that is not a movie, but it is a new kind of cinematic novel game in which time flows like a movie.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is a novel game with no particular options, but we hope you will enjoy the music, illustrations, and story.</p>",
